	<t3>
		<base>base</base>
	</t3>
	<description>
		<![CDATA[
			<div class="overview-header">
			<h2>
			  <small style="display: block;">Responsive Joomla movie template for Joomla 2.5. and Joomla 3 - <strong>JA Obelisk</strong>.</small>
			</h2>
			<p>A dedicated responsive Joomla template for any movie lover, featuring a complete theme for Christmas as a bonus point,
			Structured with clean and well organized blocks & modules, this Joomla movie template will help you deliver your content in the most professional and impressive way.</p>
			<p>Built on the robust T3 Framework with Bootstrap at core, this template is fullly responsive and RTL language layout compatible.</p>
			<p><strong>JA Obelisk</strong> features EasyBlog, K2, Off-Canvas navigation for mobile and tablet and a number of bonus pages</p>
		  </div>
				]]>
	</description>
